  <section>
    <div class="flow" style="--flow-space: var(--space-s);">
      <h2 class="heading-l">Usage</h2>
      <p>Reference the tokens directly on any element that creates a stacking context:</p>
      <pre><code>/* Navigation bar — stays above page content when scrolling */
  .site-header {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: var(--z-sticky);
  }

  /* Modal backdrop */
  .modal-backdrop {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: var(--z-modal-backdrop);
    background: rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5);
  }

  /* Modal dialog */
  .dialog {
    position: fixed;
    inset-inline: auto;
    z-index: var(--z-modal);
  }

  /* Tooltip */
  [data-tooltip]::after {
    position: absolute;
    z-index: var(--z-tooltip);
  }

  /* Toast notifications */
  .toast-region {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: var(--space-m);
    inset-inline-end: var(--space-m);
    z-index: var(--z-notification);
  }</code></pre>
      <div class="callout wide" data-variant="brand" role="note"><p>Note that <code>--z-modal-backdrop</code> (50) and <code>--z-modal</code> (51) are intentionally consecutive so the dialog always sits directly above its own backdrop without affecting other layers. Do not place other components in this range.</p></div>
  
    </div>
